title: "Knowledge Graph-Enhanced LoRA Fine-Tuning for Intelligent 3GPP-Compliant 5G Network Slicing"
version: 1.0.0
date-released: 2026-04-04
url: "https://github.com/senthilv83/LLM-FineTuning"
keywords:
  - 5G Network Slicing
