abstract: "This project implements an end-to-end, optimized pipeline for 5G Network Slicing recommendation systems. It uniquely integrates Knowledge Graph (KG) construction with Large Language Model (LLM) fine-tuning (LoRA) to create a domain-specific AI agent mapping real-world telemetry to 3GPP standards."
